author: Chris Waddell
title: Chris Waddell
text: Very bad service all round I got ink for a brother printer over a month ago the black did not work so got sent another pack still did not work but my one still works I then was asked to send back both packs and I would get credit on my account to get ink for a different printer that has not happen and now I don't even get a respond to emails about following it up so this is why I give u a bad report oh fill free to follow this up as I.m still waiting RE: #11236395 Re: #11189026 Re: #11188946 Re: #11041898 Re: #11041717 Re: #11041365 Ink RE: #11324307
